short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Grab details from all videos from a Youtube channel

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Grab details of a Youtube channel, and all its videos, WITHOUT ANY API!
The extension just scrolls down with a timeout, and parses the details directly from the webpage.
Data from the page will be saved to the clipboard as minimized JSON. You can paste it anywhere after.
Note: Some data, like date uploaded might not be totally accurate. This is because it's not possible to capture them from the channel page.
Please contribute to https://github.com/surajk95/yt-channel-grabber
to make this extension better.
